{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-df0ac465-905d-4027-ae5f-ac7d0c814d96-10\nfc_f273ff83-ea75-91c9-b748-eb69e9aef38f_0","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/规范改进需求.md","offset":80,"limit":80},"result":{"success":{"content":"\n| 域 | store 落点（建议） | shell（建议） |\n|----|-------------------|---------------|\n| 壳偏好 | `stores/shell/studioV2Store`（或保留现文件，禁止扩业务切片） | layout shell（可选） |\n| 故事编辑器 | `stores/storyEditor/` | `shellBis/storyEditor/storyEditor.shell.bis.ts` |\n| 角色库 | `stores/characters/` | `shellBis/characters/characters.shell.bis.ts` |\n| 用户库 | `stores/users/` | `shellBis/users/users.shell.bis.ts` |\n| 资源库 | `stores/assets/` | `shellBis/assets/assets.shell.bis.ts` |\n| 包列表 | `stores/packages/` | `shellBis/packages/packages.shell.bis.ts` |\n| 调试器 | `stores/debugger/` | `shellBis/debugger/debugger.shell.bis.ts` |\n\n- **禁止**多域业务态塞进同一个上帝 store。  \n- store 只结果型 action；禁网络、禁 `next/navigation`、禁 import bis。\n\n### 3.2 分层与门禁\n\n| 层 | 必须 | 禁止 |\n|----|------|------|\n| UI | 调 bis；纯 UI `useState` | 直读 store、直引 ajaxProxy |\n| feature bis | 读/写本域 store、ajaxProxy、toast | `next/navigation`；value import UI |\n| shell bis | 灌本域 store；听 `*RefreshStamp` | 一类页挂多次；代替每个按钮 |\n| *Flow.ts | 导航等路由副作用 | 命名成 `.bis.ts` |\n\n硬门禁：`STUDIO-STRUCT-021`～`024`。本批每完成一域，须从 `studio-v2-layering-baseline.json` **移除已合规文件**（或整表重扫后只剩未迁域）。\n\n### 3.3 故事编辑器双层\n\n| 项 | 口径 |\n|----|------|\n| 画布 | React Flow 自管高频 nodes/edges/transform |\n| 同步 | throttle + 松手 / 属性提交 / 切选中 **flush**；禁仅靠裸 interval |\n| store | conf、卡投影、exits、浮窗业务态、save/validate、dirty |\n| 保存 | **先 flush** → 以 store 投影 `editorGraphToBundle`；禁止有时读 canvasApi 有时读 store |\n| 属性面板 | bis 写 store → patch 画布（或订 store 结构切片） |\n\n### 3.4 库页（角色 / 用户 / 资源 / 包）同构模板\n\n```text\nshell：打开页 → GET 列表 → applyLoadResult → store\nfeature：create / save / delete → ajax → bumpRefreshStamp 或 patch 列表\nUI：列表+详情+Modal 只绑 bis；选中 id 在 store\n```\n\n删除确认、FormModal 开合可为组件瞬时态。\n\n### 3.5 调试器\n\n- Session 快照、Board 摘要、mailbox 未读等进 `debugger` store。  \n- mock 数据经 bis/ajaxProxy，**禁止** `DebuggerShell` 直引 mock 模块当长期真源。  \n- 不在本批强制 Host 全真会话（与现调试范围一致）；结构先对齐。\n\n---\n\n## 4. 刀序与依赖\n\n```text\nV2-LY-0   约定 Provider / 空 shellBis 骨架（可与 B 合并）\nV2-LY-1～4  故事编辑器（双层 + 拆 shell/feature + 保存 flush + 出 baseline）\nV2-LY-5～6  角色库\nV2-LY-7～9  用户 / 资源 / 包列表\nV2-LY-10   调试器\nV2-LY-11   工作台 / 设置扫尾\nV2-LY-12   baseline 清零或仅剩声明豁免 + 验收\n```\n\n**禁止跳步：** 未完成编辑器 flush 契约就宣称「编辑器已分层」。  \n库页可在编辑器中段并行，但 gbx `group: order` 默认串行；若拆并行须人工保证不共改同一 hook 树。\n\n---\n\n## 5. 验收标准\n\n- [ ] 各主域存在独立 `stores/<domain>/`，无跨域业务切片混存  \n- [ ] 各主域有且仅有一处页级 `*.shell.bis.ts` 灌数  \n- [ ] 目标页 UI 无 `ajaxProxy` / `stores` 直引（STRUCT-021）  \n- [ ] 故事编辑器：flush 后保存与打开 roundtrip；dirty 含未同步画布变更  \n- [ ] `studio-v2-layering-baseline.json` 本批目标文件已移除（理想：`files` 为空）  \n- [ ] `npm run quality:studio` 绿  \n- [ ] 技术设计 21 §10/§11 勾选推进；无 `@deprecated` 迁移壳残留  \n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":176,"fileSize":7728,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/规范改进需求.md","readRange":{"startLine":80,"endLine":159},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-df0ac465-905d-4027-ae5f-ac7d0c814d96-10\nfc_f273ff83-ea75-91c9-b748-eb69e9aef38f_0","startedAtMs":"1784806373793","completedAtMs":"1784806373991"},"model_call_id":"49197619-e07a-419a-b989-d21a0cf7eab8-3-kh0f","session_id":"ae50ee7b-0275-49ac-a69d-40e90d9c1aca","timestamp_ms":1784806373980}
{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-df0ac465-905d-4027-ae5f-ac7d0c814d96-11\nfc_f273ff83-ea75-91c9-b748-eb69e9aef38f_1","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/src/stores/users/usersStore.ts"},"result":{"success":{"content":"/**\n\t* 用户库域账本（Zustand）。\n\t* 切片：列表 / 选中 / loading·loadError / refreshStamp；只结果型 write。\n\t* 禁网络、禁 import bis / ajaxProxy / next/navigation（STRUCT-022）。\n\t* 灌账在 shellBis；CRUD 编排在 pageBis；本文件不挂 UI。\n\t*/\nimport { create } from \"zustand\";\nimport type { UserProfileSummary } from \"@studio-v2/typeFiles/library/users/userProfileSummary\";\nimport type { UsersLoadResult } from \"@studio-v2/typeFiles/library/users/store/usersStoreState\";\n\n/**\n\t* 刷新后选中 id：优先 preferSelectedId / 旧选中，否则首项。\n\t* 纯函数；供 applyListLoadResult 与单测共用。\n\t*/\nexport function pickUsersSelectedId(\n\tlist: readonly UserProfileSummary[],\n\tpreferId: string | undefined,\n\tprevSelectedId: string,\n): string {\n\tconst want = preferId ?? prevSelectedId;\n\tif (want !== \"\" && list.some((u) => u.userId === want)) {\n\t\treturn want;\n\t}\n\treturn list[0]?.userId ?? \"\";\n}\n\nexport type UsersStoreState = {\n\t/** 列表投影；非 Profile 全文 */\n\tprofiles: UserProfileSummary[];\n\t/** 当前选中 userId；空串表示无选中 */\n\tselectedId: string;\n\t/** 列表 GET 进行中 */\n\tloading: boolean;\n\t/** 列表加载失败人话；成功时 undefined */\n\tloadError: string | undefined;\n\t/**\n\t\t* shell 有界重拉计数。\n\t\t* feature bump 后 shell 再拉；store 自身不发请求。\n\t\t*/\n\trefreshStamp: number;\n\t/**\n\t\t* 下次成功加载时优先选中的 userId。\n\t\t* create 成功后写入，load 成功消费后清掉。\n\t\t*/\n\tpreferSelectedId: string | undefined;\n\n\t/** shell 开始拉列表：清错误、置 loading */\n\tapplyListLoadStarted: () => void;\n\t/** shell 拉列表结果：成功灌列表并解析选中；失败只记 loadError */\n\tapplyListLoadResult: (result: UsersLoadResult) => void;\n\t/** UI 经 bis 切换选中 */\n\tsetSelectedId: (userId: string) => void;\n\t/**\n\t\t* 详情保存 / 创建后的单条 upsert。\n\t\t* 不碰 refreshStamp；调用方若需全量重拉应另 bump。\n\t\t*/\n\tapplyUserUpsertResult: (summary: UserProfileSummary) => void;\n\t/** feature 请求下次加载优先选中某 id（常与 bump 连用） */\n\tsetPreferSelectedId: (userId: string | undefined) => void;\n\t/** feature 请求 shell 有界重拉 */\n\tbumpUsersRefreshStamp: () => void;\n\t/** 离页或强制清空会话 */\n\tresetUsersSession: () => void;\n};\n\nfunction createUsersSessionSlice(): Pick<\n\tUsersStoreState,\n\t| \"profiles\"\n\t| \"selectedId\"\n\t| \"loading\"\n\t| \"loadError\"\n\t| \"preferSelectedId\"\n> {\n\treturn {\n\t\tprofiles: [],\n\t\tselectedId: \"\",\n\t\tloading: false,\n\t\tloadError: undefined,\n\t\tpreferSelectedId: undefined,\n\t};\n}\n\nexport const useUsersStore = create<UsersStoreState>((set) => ({\n\t...createUsersSessionSlice(),\n\trefreshStamp: 0,\n\n\tapplyListLoadStarted() {\n\t\tset({\n\t\t\tloading: true,\n\t\t\tloadError: undefined,\n\t\t});\n\t},\n\n\tapplyListLoadResult(result) {\n\t\tif (!result.ok) {\n\t\t\tset({\n\t\t\t\tloading: false,\n\t\t\t\tloadError: result.message,\n\t\t\t\tprofiles: [],\n\t\t\t\tselectedId: \"\",\n\t\t\t});\n\t\t\treturn;\n\t\t}\n\t\tset(function (prev) {\n\t\t\tconst list = [...result.profiles];\n\t\t\tconst selectedId = pickUsersSelectedId(\n\t\t\t\tlist,\n\t\t\t\tprev.preferSelectedId,\n\t\t\t\tprev.selectedId,\n\t\t\t);\n\t\t\treturn {\n\t\t\t\tloading: false,\n\t\t\t\tloadError: undefined,\n\t\t\t\tprofiles: list,\n\t\t\t\tselectedId,\n\t\t\t\tpreferSelectedId: undefined,\n\t\t\t};\n\t\t});\n\t},\n\n\tsetSelectedId(userId) {\n\t\tset({ selectedId: userId });\n\t},\n\n\tapplyUserUpsertResult(summary) {\n\t\tset(function (prev) {\n\t\t\tconst idx = prev.profiles.findIndex(\n\t\t\t\t(u) => u.userId === summary.userId,\n\t\t\t);\n\t\t\tconst next =\n\t\t\t\tidx < 0\n\t\t\t\t\t? [...prev.profiles, summary]\n\t\t\t\t\t: prev.profiles.map(function (u, i) {\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\treturn i === idx ? summary : u;\n\t\t\t\t\t\t});\n\t\t\treturn {\n\t\t\t\tprofiles: next,\n\t\t\t\tselectedId: summary.userId,\n\t\t\t};\n\t\t});\n\t},\n\n\tsetPreferSelectedId(userId) {\n\t\tset({ preferSelectedId: userId });\n\t},\n\n\tbumpUsersRefreshStamp() {\n\t\tset(function (prev) {\n\t\t\treturn { refreshStamp: prev.refreshStamp + 1 };\n\t\t});\n\t},\n\n\tresetUsersSession() {\n\t\tset(function (prev) {\n\t\t\treturn {\n\t\t\t\t...createUsersSessionSlice(),\n\t\t\t\trefreshStamp: prev.refreshStamp,\n\t\t\t};\n\t\t});\n\t},\n}));\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":162,"fileSize":4076,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/src/stores/users/usersStore.ts","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":162},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-df0ac465-905d-4027-ae5f-ac7d0c814d96-11\nfc_f273ff83-ea75-91c9-b748-eb69e9aef38f_1","startedAtMs":"1784806373849","completedAtMs":"1784806374041"},"model_call_id":"49197619-e07a-419a-b989-d21a0cf7eab8-3-kh0f","session_id":"ae50ee7b-0275-49ac-a69d-40e90d9c1aca","timestamp_ms":1784806374024}
